after install Docker
permission required due to ubuntu user didnt add to docker group or not used sudo
so command for that 
sudo usermod -aG <GroupName> <UserName>
sudo usermod -aG  docker ubuntu  --user ubuntu added to the Docker group

sudo systemctl status docker
sudo system restart docker 


